---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Here are some functions I implemented for the Graduate Image Processing class CS6640 at the School Of Computing, University of Utah during the Fall semester 2012.

There are histogram basic operations, basic filtering, convolution, pattern detection based on cross correlation, Hough Transform, Affine Image Registration, An active contour implementation using Variation Calculus Approach
